name: Vancouver Umbrella Inc Auto Mini Umbrella
description: Great for commuting or travel and a secret weapon for thru-hiking, this compact umbrella folds up small and has an ultralight aluminum frame. Made by a company headquartered in Vancouver, where they know a thing or two about rain.Made of quick drying synthetic Pongee umbrella fabric.Ultralight aluminum frame is also sturdy in the gusts.Automatic opening mechanism.Closed length is 28cm. Open diameter is 107cm.
